{"tid":621653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話咁快已經二十幾歲....開始掛住以前既生活","createTime":"2018-04-08T13:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T13:45:03.000Z","uid":78939,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2376c9905250d719d62420981cc3d07528de54fa","tid":621653,"uid":78939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:29:51.000Z","msg":"話咁快已經20歲，上到大學，好似好好，但根本為讀而讀，漫無目的咁，開始討厭依家既生活，開始掛住以前既生活，開始掛住以前既小學中學既美好時光。<br />\n<br />\n諗翻起以前，突然間好想搵下班同學，睇下佢地點樣，會唔會有人已經結左婚生左仔。所以想約下佢地出黎食下飯，聚下舊。<br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK SEARCH 下佢地個名，個陣先發現好多人都已經失去左聯絡，唔知點先搵得到佢地。<br />\n<br />\n搵本紀念冊出黎，睇下佢地寫左啲乜，先發現個陣唔係好多人有電話，所以留底聯絡電話既人小之又小，見到有email ，即刻狗衝 SEND EMAIL 問句 : how do you do 。 好可惜既係只有google 比我既message : 找不到地址。 唔知係改左email 定係del 左。<br />\n<br />\n個人突然好感慨，個心那住那住咁，以前既朋友就咁就無左，失去左聯絡，好想搵翻你地，但完全無方法用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86392c6783cf229b3d752b18a3cf56ed7da1882e","tid":621653,"uid":78939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f88b625acdaea3b3acf2ddb2a6b815156e9c87","tid":621653,"uid":78939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:36:35.000Z","msg":"有無人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362cfe6d482a6474b0821fcdd269b28f6bacccad","tid":621653,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3db92728618e1dbefda0b5502f8